# Day 8 – Daily Notes App 📓

## What it does
A terminal-based journaling app that saves notes
with today's date automatically stamped on each entry.
Notes persist to a local file between sessions.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3 (built-in only)
- datetime (built-in)
- File I/O

## How to run
python notes.py

## What I learned
- Importing and using datetime.date
- Appending timestamped entries to a file
- While True menu loop with clean error handling
- try/except FileNotFoundError

## Output
Saves notes to notes.txt with date prefix.
Displays all notes on demand.
